title: The Arts of India - from prehistoric to modern times (Art Ebook)
description:
The Arts of India: From Prehistoric to Modern Times
Charles E. Tuttle Co. | 1966 | English | 162 pages | PDF | 17.3 MB


Comprehensive books on the arts of the great Indian sub-continent number few among the world's fine art volumes. One reason for this has been the lateness of archeological research in this area, another has probably been due to the prudery of those who condemned much Indian art as pornography. Yet India's arts are infinitely more lively than those of Egypt or Sumer, equally awe-inspiring, and just as ancient. A book to bring this great art to the attention of students and art lovers has long been needed
